snippet.title: Delysium Gameplay and cuts from new Season 1
snippet.description:
A long time awaited Season 1 started on 29th October and is ongoing till the end of the year. Join us, survivors at https://discord.gg/delysium.
More media and exciting information you can find on my Twitter page as well https://twitter.com/neapolskiy
